WEBVTT

00:09:28.800 --> 00:09:31.120
(Applause)

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:36.040
And 10 different countries.

00:09:37.160 --> 00:09:40.176
We are constantly translating the book
into different languages

00:09:40.200 --> 00:09:42.936
and collaborating with local organizations

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:45.616
to make this book available
in different countries.

00:09:45.640 --> 00:09:48.576
15 schools in different parts of India

00:09:48.600 --> 00:09:52.016
have made this book
a part of their school curriculum

00:09:52.040 --> 00:09:53.816
to teach girls about menstruation.

00:09:53.840 --> 00:09:56.240
(Applause)